===============================================
PDF NAHI BAN RAHI? YE KARO (1 MINUTE)
===============================================

PROBLEM: Frontend wrong port pe backend ko call kar raha hai

SOLUTION (Copy-Paste):

1. .env file kholo (root folder mein)

2. Ye line add karo ya update karo:

   VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

3. Frontend restart karo:
   - Terminal mein Ctrl+C
   - Phir: npm run dev

4. Browser hard refresh:
   - Ctrl + Shift + R

5. Try again:
   - Files upload karo
   - Execute karo
   - Save & Download click karo

===============================================
BACKEND CHECK:
===============================================

Backend terminal mein ye dikha raha hai:
ðŸš€ Neuro360 Backend Server running on port 5000

Matlab port 5000 hai!

Lekin frontend 3001 pe dhundh raha tha.

Ab .env mein 5000 set karne ke baad sahi hoga!

===============================================
GEMINI API KEY BHI ZAROORI HAI:
===============================================

.env file mein ye bhi hona chahiye:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your-actual-gemini-key

Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey

===============================================
COMPLETE .env FILE SAMPLE:
===============================================

# Root folder mein .env file

VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...your-key-here

# Supabase (optional)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

